title: Cloak golden gate — darkness in the bar
story: cloak-of-darkness
description: The Foyer Bar is dark while the player has the cloak
  (`a room, dark while the player has the velvet cloak`), the stumble
  rule fires on dark entry, the message is out of scope in the dark, and
  hanging the cloak lights the bar. ADR-210 AC-1 golden gate (frozen
  2026-07-10).

# Note: this file's first dark entry moves the message to `trampled`
# (first-time ordinal in the stumble rule). Reading outcomes for each
# state are asserted in the message-*.transcript files.
---

# Enter the bar wearing the cloak: dark, and the stumble phrase fires
> south
[OK: contains "Blundering around in the dark isn't a good idea!"]

> look
[OK: contains "pitch dark"]
[OK: not contains "message scrawled in the sawdust"]

# The message is not in scope while dark
> read message
[OK: contains "can't see"]

